You can't.

255
00:15:49,437 --> 00:15:50,677
See?

256
00:15:51,190 --> 00:15:53,625
Just keep your mouth shut.

257
00:16:04,703 --> 00:16:06,731
By granting these favors,

258
00:16:07,207 --> 00:16:08,937
