259
00:16:09,147 --> 00:16:11,557
All the things you have enjoyed until now.

260
00:16:11,657 --> 00:16:12,907
And...

261
00:16:13,507 --> 00:16:15,747
And all the things
that you will enjoy in the future.

262
00:16:32,117 --> 00:16:33,467
What is it?

263
00:16:33,567 --> 00:16:35,261
What do you have to give to us in secret?

264
00:16:36,471 --> 00:16:37,447
February 2000

265
00:16:37,547 --> 00:16:38,387
Is this it?

266
00:16:40,359 --> 00:16:41,317
No.

267
00:16:44,596 --> 00:16:45,897
Never mind.

268
00:16:54,165 --> 00:16:55,477
I can do it.

269
00:16:56,452 --> 00:16:58,805
Even if I lose everything,
