306
00:20:01,597 --> 00:20:05,527
To the direction that
enrages the nation the most...

307
00:20:05,627 --> 00:20:08,367
You must be happy your father's alive.
Because of the unreasonable...

308
00:20:08,467 --> 00:20:12,636
Afraid of nine deaths...
The public's rage...

309
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:23,707
These text messages are...

310
00:20:26,758 --> 00:20:28,747
between Ms Song and Bum-jo's mother?

311
00:20:29,584 --> 00:20:30,424
Yeah.

312
00:20:35,577 --> 00:20:37,267
Just because of these texts...

313
00:20:40,288 --> 00:20:42,047
my father became a criminal.

314
00:20:43,778 --> 00:20:45,543
Just because of few lines of these texts.

315
00:20:47,827 --> 00:20:49,207
Yeah.

316
00:20:49,946 --> 00:20:51,441
They made it that way...

317
00:20:52,884 --> 00:20:54,337
