318
00:21:05,527 --> 00:21:07,194
Oh, no!

319
00:21:10,757 --> 00:21:12,396
Dal-Po, your hand...

320
00:21:15,426 --> 00:21:16,266
Are you alright?

321
00:21:17,711 --> 00:21:19,007
You're bleeding too much.

322
00:21:47,316 --> 00:21:48,442
Does Bum-Jo know about this too?

323
00:21:50,872 --> 00:21:53,242
Yeah. It seemed like he was quite shocked.

324
00:21:55,267 --> 00:21:56,564
What about you?

325
00:21:57,837 --> 00:21:59,127
Are you alright?

326
00:22:01,239 --> 00:22:02,987
I'd be lying if I said I was.

327
00:22:05,299 --> 00:22:07,344
I'm sure you're angry right now
