328
00:22:08,285 --> 00:22:10,467
It's impossible to report this from MSC.

329
00:22:11,132 --> 00:22:12,307
As you can see,

330
00:22:12,681 --> 00:22:14,464
it concerns both the chief
and the director.

331
00:22:16,016 --> 00:22:18,037
It's too difficult to go through
all that and report it.

332
00:22:21,854 --> 00:22:23,177
So you do it.

333
00:22:23,869 --> 00:22:25,037
Please do it for me.

334
00:22:28,651 --> 00:22:30,079
What did Chief Song Cha-ok say?

335
00:22:30,942 --> 00:22:32,617
She admitted that all of it was true.

336
00:22:33,337 --> 00:22:35,667
But she said I can't report it
at MSC no matter what.

337
00:22:37,010 --> 00:22:38,357
That's I'm handing it over to you.

338
00:22:41,357 --> 00:22:42,623
You can do it, right?

339
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:46,547
I have to.

340
00:22:47,791 --> 00:22:51,287
No matter what... At all cost...

341
00:22:56,699 --> 00:22:57,609
Thank you.

342
00:23:01,251 --> 00:23:02,707
Thank you for handing it over to me.

343
00:24:12,327 --> 00:24:14,547
-Bum-Jo.
-Yeah.

344
00:24:15,099 --> 00:24:16,935
Did you ask your mother
about the text messages?

345
00:24:17,026 --> 00:24:17,927
What did she say?

346
00:24:18,656 --> 00:24:20,144
Why should I tell you?

347
00:24:24,997 --> 00:24:26,087
Should I give you an advice?

348
00:24:26,716 --> 00:24:29,817
No matter what you and Ha-myung do,
it won't really affect my mother.

349
00:24:30,450 --> 00:24:32,386
So don't waste your energy
on useless things

350
00:24:32,477 --> 00:24:34,017
and keep your positions.

351
00:24:35,909 --> 00:24:38,457
-What?
-I'm going to return to where I belong.

352
00:25:09,212 --> 00:25:11,218
-Captain.
-Let me drink this.

353
00:25:13,096 --> 00:25:14,187
Yes, sir.

354
00:25:17,498 --> 00:25:18,481
Thanks.

355
00:25:26,406 --> 00:25:29,297
-Who reported these texts to you?
-It was reporter Choi In-ha.

356
00:25:30,092 --> 00:25:32,697
I heard that she confirmed it
with Chief Song Cha-ok.

357
00:25:33,183 --> 00:25:35,067
If these texts are true...

358
00:25:35,556 --> 00:25:38,568
the connections between MSC executives,
Chairwoman Park Rosa

359
00:25:38,659 --> 00:25:41,384
the Assemblymen started
at least 14 years ago.

360
00:25:42,192 --> 00:25:43,058
Yes.

361
00:25:44,666 --> 00:25:46,429
Ki Ha-myung, leave your assigned position
for now.

362
00:25:46,656 --> 00:25:48,870
You cover the story
and report it yourself.

363
00:25:48,961 --> 00:25:49,801
Yes, Captain.

364
00:25:50,256 --> 00:25:52,495
Jang Hyun-gyu.
Yoon Yoo-Rae and Cha Woo-chul.

365
00:25:52,586 --> 00:25:54,731
-You guys come here and work on this also.
-Yes, Captain.

366
00:25:54,822 --> 00:25:56,418
-Yes, Captain.
-Yes, Captain.

367
00:25:59,666 --> 00:26:03,327
This is an incident from 14 years ago.
