369
00:26:08,792 --> 00:26:14,247
Ki Ha-myung. Go see Chairwoman Park Rosa
and confirm that she exchanged the texts.

370
00:26:14,829 --> 00:26:16,105
Jang Hyun-gyu.

371
00:26:16,196 --> 00:26:20,093
Find out the cause of the fire
