372
00:26:20,184 --> 00:26:21,597
Yoon Yoo-Rae and Cha Woo-chul.

373
00:26:21,688 --> 00:26:24,907
Find out how the direction of reporting
changed after these texts were exchanged.

374
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,977
We must report...

