436
00:30:36,906 --> 00:30:38,772
Were you fired?

437
00:30:39,565 --> 00:30:41,555
No. I quit.

438
00:30:42,609 --> 00:30:47,077
I quit so that I can tell the truth,
like you.

439
00:30:56,265 --> 00:30:57,433
How did you feel, dad?

440
00:30:58,177 --> 00:31:00,557
Did you regret after you quit?

441
00:31:03,806 --> 00:31:04,646
In-ha.

