444
00:31:11,944 --> 00:31:13,318
Tell me I did the right thing.

445
00:31:16,475 --> 00:31:19,435
Please, tell me
I did the right thing, dad.

446
00:31:29,328 --> 00:31:30,347
You did the right thing.

447
00:31:31,586 --> 00:31:32,867
My daughter did the right thing.

448
00:31:39,911 --> 00:31:41,787
Mom...

449
00:31:45,227 --> 00:31:47,327
Mom...

450
00:32:13,274 --> 00:32:14,842
Chairwoman Park Rosa.
