452
00:32:17,910 --> 00:32:19,078
You can't do this.

453
00:32:19,608 --> 00:32:21,025
Oh, my? Who is this?

454
00:32:21,506 --> 00:32:22,573
Aren't you reporter Ki Ha-myung?

455
00:32:22,856 --> 00:32:25,070
-It's your friend, right?
-Yes.

456
00:32:26,029 --> 00:32:27,707
It's alright since he's my son's friend.

457
00:32:34,038 --> 00:32:36,327
