00:32:41,667 --> 00:32:43,811
Yes. I'll continue to ask you.

461
00:32:44,416 --> 00:32:46,205
You said that this person in the text
should be hidden.

462
00:32:46,295 --> 00:32:48,297
You asked for this person
to not be mentioned as guilty.

463
00:32:48,616 --> 00:32:49,852
Who is this person here?

464
00:32:50,364 --> 00:32:52,657
