00:33:18,154 --> 00:33:20,765
I just can't remember
what you're talking about.

475
00:33:23,292 --> 00:33:25,286
I didn't say that it was a long time ago.

476
00:33:31,276 --> 00:33:32,337
We got her.

477
00:33:33,145 --> 00:33:34,530
You said you can't remember,

478
00:33:34,621 --> 00:33:36,879
but you do remember
that this is from a long time ago.

479
00:33:37,868 --> 00:33:39,018
I'll ask you again.

480
00:33:39,703 --> 00:33:43,474
Did you exchange texts with
Chief Song Cha-ok of MSC 14 years ago?

481
00:33:44,936 --> 00:33:46,727
-Get rid of him.
